WHAT:
A skimmable, append-only decision log — CHANGELOG.md at the repo root, newest-first.
Each entry: Why (prose) · Chose/Rejected · Files (read from git) · Open. Captures the
reasoning a diff cannot hold; complements git history, does not restate it.

